{"tid":1911795,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郵輪「歌劇號」有乘客意大利落船後確診 全船2000人要隔離觀察","createTime":"2020-03-05T14:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T15:30:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06ddcd65e2c0bc6e3c78a1cf3c3f4ce2d1e96ca6","tid":1911795,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"地中海郵輪「歌劇號」（MSC Opera）一名乘客近日在意大利下船後確診武漢肺炎，船長告訴全船超過2,000人不能離開，要接受隔離觀察，以「安全理由」將上岸的乘客召回。<br />\n<br />\n各國政府因應疫情迅速變更旅遊限制，這艘郵輪的航行路線已因此改了兩次。船長發信給乘客說：「我剛剛得知，也想讓你們馬上知道，奧地利衞生當局跟接觸通知我們，一名上周坐『歌劇號』跟我們同行的前乘客確診武漢肺炎。這名奧地利籍男乘客，於上周五在意大利熱那亞（Genoa）下船，目前正在回奧地利路上。」<br />\n<br />\n「明確地說，此人並不在船上。我們仍在等待奧地利衞生當局進一步說明和指引，也與希臘當局聯繫上。不過，我們積極採取各種預防措施，確保乘客安全。所有乘客和船員被要求留在船上，直至我們就此事有更清晰資料位置。」船長表示乘客無須擔心，因為無跡象顯示郵輪上目前有任何問題，也沒有病例顯示船上會有確診者。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200305/CSC4X7GZNRVCQEI2SPMVK6GBGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200305%2FCSC4X7GZNRVCQEI2SPMVK6GBGI%2F&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=d691bbdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200305%2FCSC4X7GZNRVCQEI2SPMVK6GBGI%2F&h=376a863e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200305/CSC4X7GZNRVCQEI2SPMVK6GBGI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbed00eae0b0c18aabeab3f2ab08a5210e00a82","tid":1911795,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"唔洗帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a048aa85ac4b75c79ca42e55964c5292994d35c1","tid":1911795,"uid":171849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會好似公主號咁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmo